INSERT INTO `reviews` (`id`, `title`, `info`, `content`, `status`, `created`, `image`) VALUES
(1, 'Travel Review: Italy Vacation, Rome, Venice, Florence, Tuscany, Boat Tour', 'This was a fabulous trip and here’s why: The Top 4 Reasons We Love this Travel Company:\r\n\r\n#4.  They Know Stuff We Don’t \r\n\r\nThe travel company\'s team’s knowledge is staggering.  Did we know not to miss the Tarot Gardens near Capalbio?  No, but they did.  They know what to do and who can help make it all...', '<div class=\"fieldset-wrapper with-legend\"><section class=\"field field-name-field-countries field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Which Country (Countries) did you visit on this trip?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\">Italy</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-summary field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Your overall comments on the trip and the travel company:&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>This was a fabulous trip and here’s why:&nbsp;The Top 4 Reasons We Love&nbsp;this Travel Company:</p>\r\n<p>#4. &nbsp;They Know Stuff We Don’t&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The travel company\'s team’s knowledge is staggering. &nbsp;Did we know not to miss the Tarot Gardens near Capalbio? &nbsp;No, but they did. &nbsp;They know what to do and who can help make it all happen. Hotels, restaurants, tour guides, extra adventures — they know how to put it all together for a smooth and memorable trip.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>#3. &nbsp;Their Relationships Are Key</p>\r\n<p>To us, even&nbsp;more important &nbsp;than a great relationship between the tour company and&nbsp;the travelers is the one&nbsp;between the&nbsp;travel company\'s staff and their preferred services, like hotels, tour guides, drivers, etc. &nbsp;Because the company seeks out and works with great businesses and individuals, the traveler gets the best. &nbsp;Do I know how to find the company that makes&nbsp;sure the water taxi is&nbsp;at our Venice hotel at 4 am&nbsp;to get&nbsp;us to the land taxi to the airport? &nbsp; No, I do not — but this travel company does, so we are covered. &nbsp;Even in the dark!</p>\r\n<p># 2. &nbsp;They Have Buying Power</p>\r\n<p>First, the company was completely respectful of our budget and priorities. &nbsp;Never felt pressured to “buy more” or upgrade constantly. </p>\r\n<p>Second, because of those relationships mentioned above, this travel company&nbsp;could give us truly wonderful options at our comfortable price point. &nbsp;Lovely hotels,&nbsp;&nbsp;amazing tour guides, and drivers&nbsp; — not likely to be affordable&nbsp;&nbsp;if we were assembling&nbsp;this trip ourselves. &nbsp;Strong partnerships between this travel company and these folks benefit the traveler most of all.</p>\r\n<p># 1 &nbsp; They Do The Right Thing</p>\r\n<p>Throughout our time working/traveling with&nbsp;this company, we always felt they were doing the right thing for all involved. &nbsp;Example: &nbsp;would we be willing to consider a different housing&nbsp;option when the favorite hotel was unexpectedly unavailable due to renovation? Great revised plan benefitted all, so good to go. &nbsp;Could the company help us with train tickets when thanks to hurricane in our area, we were dealing with suddenly homeless family members and wonky internet? Of course! &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The old&nbsp;saying “ You will never go wrong doing the right thing” is spot on and really is the core of this travel company\'s business model. &nbsp;And who benefits? Everyone involved, including these two lucky Texas travelers.</p>\r\n</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-best-parts field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">What were the most enjoyable or memorable parts of your trip?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>The ability to balance the freedom and independence we wanted with the guidance and expertise of true travel professionals was key for us. &nbsp;Driving around Tuscany on our own was glorious, but we could do that because&nbsp;&nbsp;the travel company gave us the route&nbsp;and the stops. Having logistics taken care of made this trip worry-free and so much more enjoyable.</p>\r\n<p>Tours in Florence and Venice with excellent guides were highlights. &nbsp;The boat tour in Venice gave us the chance to see&nbsp;so much more beyond the tourist paths.</p>\r\n</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-do-differently field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">If you could take your trip again, what would you do differently?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>Nothing. &nbsp;We would call this company, have our planning conversations, and let the experts go do the work.</p>\r\n</div></div></section></div>', 1, 2147483647, 'vastautumnvineyardsoftuscany.famouswineregionchiantiitaly.jpg'),
(2, 'Italy Trip Review: Venice, Florence, Rome, Milan, Bellagio, Lake Como', 'I truly do not have the words to express the amazing vacation that was planned for us by this travel agent and his staff. My husband and I have very busy schedules so I knew we would need help planning our trip, but I wasn’t sure who I could trust. After many internet searches and conversations with other travel...', '<div class=\"fieldset-wrapper with-legend\"><section class=\"field field-name-field-countries field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Which Country (Countries) did you visit on this trip?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\">Italy</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-summary field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Your overall comments on the trip and the travel company:&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>I truly do not have the words to express the amazing vacation that was planned for us by this travel agent and his staff. My husband and I have very busy schedules so I knew we would need help planning our trip, but I wasn’t sure who I could trust. After many internet searches and conversations with other travel agents I knew without a doubt that we had to go with this agent and his team. His itinerary, travel suggestions and prompt responses blew me away and did not disappoint.</p>\r\n<p>While planning the trip (and on the trip) our representatives were always available to me to answer any questions I had. This was truly one of the most enjoyable experiences I have ever had working with a travel partner.</p>\r\n<p>Every amenity did not disappoint.&nbsp; From the hotels, to the cars, to the guides-they were all 5 star and exceptional!&nbsp; Every guide we hired for private tours were punctual, knowledgeable and courteous. Having the guides was a lifesaver because they knew the best restaurants in town and all the of the best shopping not to mention being able to skip all the busy lines!</p>\r\n<p>This vacation was truly a vacation of a life time for my husband and me. Every day I was amazed by what I saw, what I ate and all the new places we went.&nbsp; We made great memories that will last a lifetime and I am beyond grateful to our agent for helping us make all these amazing memories!</p>\r\n</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-best-parts field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">What were the most enjoyable or memorable parts of your trip?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>We absolutely loves the day trip to Tuscany and having lunch at the winery. It was such a relaxing day looking at all of the beautiful scenery and having&nbsp;a private lunch in the winery\'s barrel room. I would also highly suggest, the day trip to Como from Bellagio. Como is a breathtaking city with water views to die for.</p>\r\n</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-do-differently field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">If you could take your trip again, what would you do differently?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>I think next time we would have taken the trip to Parma as opposed to taking the train and skipping it. Other than that I would not have changed one thing!</p>\r\n</div></div></section></div>', 1, 2147483647, 'meg1.jpg'),
(3, 'Travel Review: Luxury Trip to Italy, Rome, Positano, Venice', 'We just returned home from a two week trip to Italy and the most amazing time of our lives! Our travel agent planned such a romantic and wonderful trip for us, everything was absolutely perfect! I had never traveled out of the country before and I was hesitant to book with someone that I could not meet with in...', '<div class=\"fieldset-wrapper with-legend\"><section class=\"field field-name-field-countries field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Which Country (Countries) did you visit on this trip?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\">Italy</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-summary field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Your overall comments on the trip and the travel company:&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>We just returned home from a two week trip to Italy and the most amazing time of our lives! Our travel agent planned such a romantic and wonderful trip for us, everything was absolutely perfect! I had never traveled out of the country before and I was hesitant to book with someone that I could not meet with in person, but after doing some online research I am so happy that we found Zicasso! Zicasso matched us with this travel company&nbsp;who we then worked with to plan the entire trip.&nbsp; It was the best decision we could have made! Working with someone who knew firsthand all of the areas we wanted to visit and who knew the best hotels, restaurants, guides, drivers, essentially someone who had the “inside track” on everything, was the best decision we could have made! Our agent was amazing and made all of my dreams come true! While we were in Italy, we saw so many travelers who had issues with their reservations and travel, we had absolutely not one single thing go wrong during the entire two weeks.&nbsp; Everything was booked in advance and we had a driver or guide working with us every step of the way, I truly felt so special during the entire trip. Italy is a spectacularly beautiful country and I feel so fortunate to have had such an amazing group of people working with us to help make our dream vacation a reality. Thank you thank you thank from the bottom of my heart to Zicasso and to our travel company for the wonderful memories I will treasure for the rest of my life! xoxo</p>\r\n</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-best-parts field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">What were the most enjoyable or memorable parts of your trip?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>We enjoyed the beautiful landscape and spectacular scenery so much! Positano and Venice were especially memorable and the hotels we stayed in there were top notch. The guides and drivers that we worked with were a large part of what made our experience so special and personal. We really appreciated all of the advance reservations, the seamless transition from location to location, hotel to hotel, and how stress free everything was for us.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-do-differently field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">If you could take your trip again, what would you do differently?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>We would do everything exactly the same. &nbsp;It was perfect in EVERY way!</p>\r\n</div></div></section></div>', 11, 2147483647, 'becky1.jpg'),
(4, 'Travel Review: Luxury Family Vacation in Italy, Rome, Florence, Tuscany, Lucca, Pisa, Orvieto, Lucca, Siena', 'My family just returned from a ten night trip to Rome and Tuscany planned by this agent and his company. Every aspect of the trip was simply perfect.\r\n\r\nI\'ve  travelled a fair amount for both work and pleasure over the past forty years, so my requirements are fairly specific. Our agent exceeded all of my...', '<div class=\"fieldset-wrapper with-legend\"><section class=\"field field-name-field-countries field-type-entityreference field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Which Country (Countries) did you visit on this trip?&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\">Italy</div></div></section><section class=\"field field-name-field-summary field-type-text-long field-label-inline clearfix view-mode-full\"><h2 class=\"field-label\">Your overall comments on the trip and the travel company:&nbsp;</h2><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\"><p>My family just returned from a&nbsp;ten night&nbsp;trip to Rome and Tuscany planned by this agent and his company. Every aspect of the trip was simply perfect.</p>\r\n<p>I\'ve&nbsp; travelled a fair amount for both work and pleasure over the past forty years, so my requirements are fairly specific. Our agent exceeded all of my expectations in planning this 60th birthday trip for my wife and entire family. Planning started over a year ago with a number of e-mails with our agent describing what we were looking for - punctual drivers,&nbsp; passionate and professional guides,&nbsp; all tickets purchased in advance, coordinating multiple travel schedules.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Our travel agent delivered on all fronts.</p>\r\n<p>Our agent suggested an itinerary almost a year ago - an itinerary that we continued to fine tune over time. Throughout that process, he was responsive - never taking more than a day to respond to detailed questions and requests for modifications. He was also the consummate professional, always patient and thoughtful, with suggestions that always improved the final product. Restaurant reservations for lunches and dinners for the entire trip were added to the final detailed itinerary.</p>\r\n<p>We agreed upon four nights in Rome and six in Tuscany. Not one driver was late for a pick-up and the guides ranged from very good to exceptional. All of the drivers and guides coordinated with each other, and all had the necessary tickets to the various sites, providing easy access without standing on lengthy lines. In Rome, special kudos go to our guide for his passionate tours of Vatican City and Ancient Rome.</p>\r\n<p>On the trip to Florence, our driver stopped in Orvieto and our guide provided a fascinating tour of the city. In the afternoon, we stopped at Barbi vineyards for a wonderful tour, lunch and wine tasting. Very intimate, educational and delicious. Probably the best vineyard experience we\'ve ever had. Our wine educator, was wonderful.</p>\r\n<p>The wonders of Florence speak for themselves - and we had a first rate guide in Ulrich. Our driver for the entire stay was personable, professional and punctual - and always in contact with the various guides. Our guide also provided a memorable tour of Pisa and Lucca, offering information about both cities that might not be found in a guidebook.&nbsp;&nbsp;An unexpected mini-concert at Pisa\'s Baptistry was a real treat. As a newly minted sommelier, our guide&nbsp;joined us for a fabulous lunch in Lucca at Borgo Antico where she continued with her &nbsp;discussion of Lucca and wine.</p>\r\n<p>We had a charming archaeologist and cyclist guide through San Gimignano, Siena and a 10KM hike in the gorgeous Val d\' Orcia from from Montalcino to Fattoria La Maggia, where we had a wonderful tour, lunch and wine tasting. It\'s worth noting that our guide rode the trail the morning before our hike to ensure that it was clear.</p>\r\n<p>One of the highlights of the trip was an evening with a personal chef, caterer and sommelier. We met her at her home where, over a three hour period, she brought her love for food to life. We learned how to cook (and eat) pasta, a delicious chicken and vegetable dish and tiramusu. She is charming.</p>\r\n<p>Bottom line, this was a trip of a lifetime. This travel agent is a patient and good listener and the guides he engaged were passionate professionals who made this such a memorable trip. This travel agent and his company have my families unconditional recommendation - and our gratitude. Grazie mille!</p>\r\n<p>Richard W</p>\r\n<p>October 13, 2017</p>\r\n</div></div></section></div>', 11, 2147483647, 'leaningtower.pisaitaly_2.jpg');

