(1, 'Huayna Potosi - can you climb a 6000 peak on Friday 13th?', 'huayna-potosi-climb-thumbnail.jpg', '<article itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\" class=\"post\">\r\n                    <div class=\"text-center post-header\">\r\n                        <a class=\"badge badge-custom\" href=\"https://www.czickontheroad.com/bolivia\" title=\"Bolivia\">Bolivia</a>\r\n                        <h1 class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"name\">\r\n                                Huayna Potosi - can you climb a 6000 peak on Friday 13th?                        </h1>\r\n\r\n                                                <span class=\"post-date\" itemprop=\"datePublished\" content=\"2018-04-13\">\r\n                            April 13, 2018                        </span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"blog-detail-intro\" itemprop=\"articleSection\">\r\n                        Huayna Potosi is one of the white peaks surrounding La Paz and finding out there are many tours for climbing it, it took us just a few days before we decided to go on this adventure. The weather was nice and we knew we are in good enough condition to manage this climb. Besides this, the thought of watching the sunrise from 6088 altitudes was just irresistible. The only thing which we didn\'t think about was the date we\'ve chosen for this climb...                    </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"post-preview\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"main-slider basic-slider owl-carousel owl-theme owl-loaded\">\r\n                                                        \r\n                                                    <div class=\"owl-stage-outer\"><div class=\"owl-stage\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); transition: 0s; width: 847.5px;\"><div class=\"owl-item active\" style=\"width: 847.5px; margin-right: 0px;\"><div class=\"main-slide\">\r\n                                <img src=\"/userfiles/im