(3, 'La Paz – a fascinating Teleferic city tour for every budget', 'la-paz-thumbnail.jpg', '<article itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Article\" class=\"post\">\r\n                    <div class=\"text-center post-header\">\r\n                        <a class=\"badge badge-custom\" href=\"https://www.czickontheroad.com/bolivia\" title=\"Bolivia\">Bolivia</a>\r\n                        <h1 class=\"post-title\" itemprop=\"name\">\r\n                                La Paz – a fascinating Teleferic city tour for every budget                        </h1>\r\n\r\n                                                <span class=\"post-date\" itemprop=\"datePublished\" content=\"2018-04-05\">\r\n                            April 5, 2018                        </span>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"blog-detail-intro\" itemprop=\"articleSection\">\r\n                        I wasn\'t very excited by visiting the city of La Paz, but I immediately fell in love with it. You won’t find here much of a beautiful colonial architecture as in other cities, but maybe that’s what makes it special and a bit different. Another thing is its fascinating public transportation – which runs in the air!                    </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"post-preview\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"main-slider basic-slider owl-carousel owl-theme owl-loaded\">\r\n                                                        \r\n                                                    <div class=\"owl-stage-outer\"><div class=\"owl-stage\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); transition: 0s; width: 847.5px;\"><div class=\"owl-item active\" style=\"width: 847.5px; margin-right: 0px;\"><div class=\"main-slide\">\r\n                                <img src=\"/userfiles/images/post/medium/la-paz-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"La Paz – a fascinating Teleferic city tour for every budget\" title=\"La Paz – a fascinating Teleferic city tour for every budget\" class=\"rounded\" itemprop=\"image\">\r\n                            </div></div></div></div><div class=\"owl-controls\"><div class=\"owl-nav\"><div class=\"owl-prev\" style=\"\">prev</div><div class=\"owl-next\" style=\"\">next</div></div><div class=\"owl-dots\" style=\"display: none;\"></div></div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"post-share\">\r\n                        <div class=\"share clearfix\">\r\n    <span class=\"share_text\">Share:</span>\r\n    <ul class=\"clearfix\">\r\n        <li>\r\n            <span class=\"mdi mdi-facebook csbuttons\" data-type=\"facebook\" displaytext=\"Facebook\"> </span>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n            <span class=\"mdi mdi-twitter csbuttons\" data-type=\"twitter\" displaytext=\"Tweet\"> </span>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n            <span class=\"mdi mdi-linkedin csbuttons\" data-type=\"linkedin\" displaytext=\"LinkedIn\"> </span>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n            <span class=\"mdi mdi-google-plus-box csbuttons\" data-type=\"google\" displaytext=\"Google +\"> </span>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li>\r\n            <span class=\"mdi mdi-pinterest csbuttons\" data-type=\"pinterest\" displaytext=\"Pinterest\"> </span>\r\n        </li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n</div>                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"blog-detail-description\">\r\n                        <div itemprop=\"articleBody\">\r\n                            <h2>La Paz - a fascinating city at the altitude of 3650 m</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The thought of visiting another huge city was quite repellent to me. I still had a clear memory of stinking and overcrowded Lima, with overpriced restaurants and bars and terrible traffic. But La Paz has surprised me, in a very positive way. Compared to Lima it is a nice and clean city, which maybe doesn\'t have much colonial architecture and green parks, but it has other advantages. Beside the mountains surrounding it, where we went for one or more day trips (read about our climb to <a href=\"https://www.czickontheroad.com/bolivia/huayna-potosi-climbing-a-6000-peak-on-friday-13th\" target=\"_blank\">Huayna Potosi</a> and unsuccessful <a href=\"https://www.czickontheroad.com/bolivia/el-choro-trek-how-the-most-popular-trek-turned-into-a-nightmare-in-the-jungle\" target=\"_blank\">El Choro trek</a>) I was mostly fascinated by their public transportation system - besides typical buses and taxis there is a cableway crossing the whole city, which shortened the transport from one side of the city to another from one hour to 10 minutes!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Browsing the city from the air</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The first thing we noticed when we have arrived at the city were the Teleferic cabins above us, which we only knew from the European ski slopes. Then our host Ricardo told us about a wonderful tour we could have by using it, seeing the whole city from the air. We couldn’t resist and spent one whole day traveling by this fascinating transportation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One ride on one line costs 3b. / 0,3€ and there are total 7 lines. In the next 12 years they plan to build another 16 lines, then it will be really possible to cruise above the city for a whole day. Now some lines are already in progress, but a round tour is not possible yet, so we had to complete the circle by foot.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Stroll through the city to the urban park</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We started our tour on a yellow line, which station was close to our hotel, then switched to blue, white, and in the end orange, where we got out and strolled through the busy city, visiting the witch market and making our way back down to Socopachi neighborhood. In the near future, the circle will be possible to finish with a brown and purple line – check the picture of the map in the gallery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On the way down we have also visited the city park Parque Urbano Central, expecting to find some nice green area to rest – well, that didn’t happen. This park is more of a concrete jungle with few green spots – those easy to find are covered by trash, the more hidden ones are occupied by young lovers. There is though one fascinating area and that’s the restricted area – of course, we went there and besides two stinking junkies found a wonderful abandoned playground with some really photogenic mosaic sculptures – definitely my highlight of the day. (Though to get out of there we had to crawl under a fence…). We finished this wonderful day tour on a Mirador in Socopachi and then in the best Vietnamese restaurant.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"galleryCzick\" data-id=\"77\" data-url=\"la-paz-tour-1\">     <div class=\"row\" rel=\"nofollow\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/1-La-Paz_104424.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"The map of Teleferic for our orientation - only later we found a paper one in a cafe in the center.\" title=\"The map of Teleferic for our orientation - only later we found a paper one in a cafe in the center.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/1-La-Paz_104424.jpg\" alt=\"The map of Teleferic for our orientation - only later we found a paper one in a cafe in the center.\">             </a>             <p>The map of Teleferic for our orientation - only later we found a paper one in a cafe in the center. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/2-La-Paz_103926.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"The yellow line - our starting point\" title=\"The yellow line - our starting point\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/2-La-Paz_103926.jpg\" alt=\"The yellow line - our starting point\">             </a>             <p>The yellow line - our starting point &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/3-La-Paz_105030.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"The view from Teleferic is really stunning.\" title=\"The view from Teleferic is really stunning.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/3-La-Paz_105030.jpg\" alt=\"The view from Teleferic is really stunning.\">             </a>             <p>The view from Teleferic is really stunning. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/4-La-Paz_105204.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"You can even see the white peaks surrounding the city\" title=\"You can even see the white peaks surrounding the city\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/4-La-Paz_105204.jpg\" alt=\"You can even see the white peaks surrounding the city\">             </a>             <p>You can even see the white peaks surrounding the city &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/5-La-Paz_105915.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"The blue line goes above a more rural area.\" title=\"The blue line goes above a more rural area.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/5-La-Paz_105915.jpg\" alt=\"The blue line goes above a more rural area.\">             </a>             <p>The blue line goes above a more rural area. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/6-La-Paz_111803.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"And the white line takes you directly between the skyscrapers.\" title=\"And the white line takes you directly between the skyscrapers.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/6-La-Paz_111803.jpg\" alt=\"And the white line takes you directly between the skyscrapers.\">             </a>             <p>And the white line takes you directly between the skyscrapers. &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/7-La-Paz_112258.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"Orange line has also some wonderful views\" title=\"Orange line has also some wonderful views\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/7-La-Paz_112258.jpg\" alt=\"Orange line has also some wonderful views\">             </a>             <p>Orange line has also some wonderful views &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/8-La-Paz_112507.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"Including a small old cemetery just before the end station.\" title=\"Including a small old cemetery just before the end station.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/8-La-Paz_112507.jpg\" alt=\"Including a small old cemetery just before the end station.\">             </a>             <p>Including a small old cemetery just before the end station. &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/9-La-Paz_115232.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"We got out from the orange line to enjoy a stroll through the city - and some orange juice.\" title=\"We got out from the orange line to enjoy a stroll through the city - and some orange juice.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/9-La-Paz_115232.jpg\" alt=\"We got out from the orange line to enjoy a stroll through the city - and some orange juice.\">             </a>             <p>We got out from the orange line to enjoy a stroll through the city - and some orange juice. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/10-La-Paz_115638.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"It can be very crowded on the streets, the Teleferic takes a huge portion of the traffic.\" title=\"It can be very crowded on the streets, the Teleferic takes a huge portion of the traffic.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/10-La-Paz_115638.jpg\" alt=\"It can be very crowded on the streets, the Teleferic takes a huge portion of the traffic.\">             </a>             <p>It can be very crowded on the streets, the Teleferic takes a huge portion of the traffic. &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/11-La-Paz_120716.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"Chinese goods are everywhere here.\" title=\"Chinese goods are everywhere here.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/11-La-Paz_120716.jpg\" alt=\"Chinese goods are everywhere here.\">             </a>             <p>Chinese goods are everywhere here. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/12-La-Paz_133414.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"And the center is bursting with overpriced cafes and restaurants.\" title=\"And the center is bursting with overpriced cafes and restaurants.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/12-La-Paz_133414.jpg\" alt=\"And the center is bursting with overpriced cafes and restaurants.\">             </a>             <p>And the center is bursting with overpriced cafes and restaurants. &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/13-La-Paz_142958.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"La Paz maybe doesn\'t have a colonial architecture, but it is a beautiful city\" title=\"La Paz maybe doesn\'t have a colonial architecture, but it is a beautiful city\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/13-La-Paz_142958.jpg\" alt=\"La Paz maybe doesn\'t have a colonial architecture, but it is a beautiful city\">             </a>             <p>La Paz maybe doesn\'t have a colonial architecture, but it is a beautiful city &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/14-La-Paz_143935.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"And this is my very favorite spot - isnt the crocodile just wonderful?\" title=\"And this is my very favorite spot - isnt the crocodile just wonderful?\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/14-La-Paz_143935.jpg\" alt=\"And this is my very favorite spot - isnt the crocodile just wonderful?\">             </a>             <p>And this is my very favorite spot - isnt the crocodile just wonderful? &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                   </div> </div>\r\n\r\n<h2>El Alto – the biggest and highest market</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>On Thursday or Sunday, there is a huge market in El Alto – a city above La Paz. To go there, we repeated the same Teleferic tour, just at the end station of orange line switched to red, which goes directly to the beginning of the market, at 4000 alt. meters. Then we went two stations by the blue line, which flies above the whole market, giving us an approximate idea how big this market really is. Though guides from the Free walking tour promised us this is a flea market, there were mostly goods from China and second-hand stuff was limited to cloths and car parts, quite disappointing…</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"galleryCzick\" data-id=\"78\" data-url=\"la-paz-tour-2\">     <div class=\"row\" rel=\"nofollow\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/15-La-Paz_120328.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"Red line goes up to the El Alto, city at 4000 alt. m.\" title=\"Red line goes up to the El Alto, city at 4000 alt. m.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/15-La-Paz_120328.jpg\" alt=\"Red line goes up to the El Alto, city at 4000 alt. m.\">             </a>             <p>Red line goes up to the El Alto, city at 4000 alt. m. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/16-La-Paz_121656.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"The blue line then takes you above the biggest market in the world.\" title=\"The blue line then takes you above the biggest market in the world.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/16-La-Paz_121656.jpg\" alt=\"The blue line then takes you above the biggest market in the world.\">             </a>             <p>The blue line then takes you above the biggest market in the world. &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/17-La-Paz_121921.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"From the air you can really appreciate its size - supposedly it covers the area of 5 square km.\" title=\"From the air you can really appreciate its size - supposedly it covers the area of 5 square km.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/17-La-Paz_121921.jpg\" alt=\"From the air you can really appreciate its size - supposedly it covers the area of 5 square km.\">             </a>             <p>From the air you can really appreciate its size - supposedly it covers the area of 5 square km. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/18-La-Paz_135428.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"Mostly there is just Chinese goods and each stands has its specialization. You can find here anything from balls...\" title=\"Mostly there is just Chinese goods and each stands has its specialization. You can find here anything from balls...\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/18-La-Paz_135428.jpg\" alt=\"Mostly there is just Chinese goods and each stands has its specialization. You can find here anything from balls...\">             </a>             <p>Mostly there is just Chinese goods and each stands has its specialization. You can find here anything from balls... &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/19-La-Paz_142150.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"...to toothpastes.\" title=\"...to toothpastes.\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/19-La-Paz_142150.jpg\" alt=\"...to toothpastes.\">             </a>             <p>...to toothpastes. &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/20-La-Paz.jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"But most importantly, don\'t forget to enjoy the street treats!\" title=\"But most importantly, don\'t forget to enjoy the street treats!\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/20-La-Paz.jpg\" alt=\"But most importantly, don\'t forget to enjoy the street treats!\">             </a>             <p>But most importantly, don\'t forget to enjoy the street treats! &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                   </div> </div>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Air tour above La Paz</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>If you get a chance to go to La Paz, don’t miss the opportunity to see the city from the Air. Start with a yellow line down to Libertador station, then switch to the blue line and go one station to switch to white. Stay on the white line till the end station, enjoying some nice views of the city, as well as the white peaks surrounding it. At the end of the white switch to orange – just before the end station is a small interesting grave ground. Switch to red line at the end station of orange and enjoy the ride up to El Alto. Then get out and stroll through the interesting streets of this blooming city – if you manage to come on Thursday or Sunday, you will be able to shop at one of the biggest markets in the world, supposedly it takes the whole 5 square km! Then go back down with the red line, get out at the end station, and stroll through the city towards the city center and Parque Urbano Central. The whole trip will cost you 18b. / 2,2€.</p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                                                                        <div class=\"mt-5\">\r\n                        <div class=\"detailsInfoBox\">\r\n                            &nbsp;<br>\r\n                            <br><h3>Location</h3>\r\n                            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"x_lat\" value=\"-16.489689\" id=\"single_lat\">\r\n                            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"x_lng\" value=\"-68.119294\" id=\"single_lng\">\r\n          