he location we were at the moment. The beer is quite OK, though not as good as the Czech one of course ;-)\">             </a>             <p>From local bears, the most popular are Cusqueno – from Cusco and Arequipeno – from Arequipa. Logically, we made the choice based on the location we were at the moment. The beer is quite OK, though not as good as the Czech one of course ;-) &nbsp;</p>         </div>              </div><div class=\"row\">                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/13 (1).jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"Many accommodation offer breakfast, this one is from our Airbnb in Ica and was the best one we had in the whole 2 months – bread, egg, butter, jam and always mango or melon and avocado. Absolutely wonderful!\" title=\"Many accommodation offer breakfast, this one is from our Airbnb in Ica and was the best one we had in the whole 2 months – bread, egg, butter, jam and always mango or melon and avocado. Absolutely wonderful!\" data-toggle=\"lightbox\" data-gallery=\"gallery\">                 <img src=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/13 (1).jpg\" alt=\"Many accommodation offer breakfast, this one is from our Airbnb in Ica and was the best one we had in the whole 2 months – bread, egg, butter, jam and always mango or melon and avocado. Absolutely wonderful!\">             </a>             <p>Many accommodation offer breakfast, this one is from our Airbnb in Ica and was the best one we had in the whole 2 months – bread, egg, butter, jam and always mango or melon and avocado. Absolutely wonderful! &nbsp;</p>         </div>                       <div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6  col-sm-6  col-xs-12\">             <a href=\"https://czickontheroad-962d.kxcdn.com/userfiles/images/post/medium/14 (1).jpg\" class=\"swipebox\" data-footer=\"You can also buy a breakfast at some local coffee places, th